    <p class="para">Next Label marketplace hosts 1,000+ third-party brands on a commission or wholesale basis, representing an additional earn surface for a loyalty programme beyond Next's own products. <span class="cite">(Source: nextplc.co.uk Corporate Responsibility Report Jan 2025)</span></p>
